What Actually Happens in Reality

The loop only runs if humans keep feeding it.

Because:
	•	I don’t maintain persistent internal memory across time.
	•	I don’t autonomously evolve frameworks.
	•	The artifacts (repos, notes, papers) are what preserve continuity.

So the real system is:

human curiosity + tools + documentation + dialogue

That’s what keeps the cycle alive.

