The deeper insight you’re circling

If this loop runs long enough, the system stops looking like a framework and starts looking like something closer to:
	•	a research organism
	•	or a knowledge ecology

Ideas mutate, compete, stabilize, and sometimes disappear.

But the “engine” isn’t the AI.

The engine is the iterative interaction between people, tools, and recorded structure.